{"tid":1084501,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來帽比分手更痛","createTime":"2019-03-30T12:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T09:47:34.000Z","uid":237038,"like":90,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a01c0740f9adc2e990178eb74f31e8d1ec3cd852","tid":1084501,"uid":237038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"以前一直以為分手已經夠痛<br />\n但原來帽係仲痛<br />\n睇住你愛既人一腳踏兩船<br />\n你視佢為你既唯一，佢視你為玩伴<br />\n一個大話接一個大話咁拆穿<br />\n睇住你若無其事講得出咁多大話<br />\n我心都寒曬<br />\n既然你有另一個<br />\n點解仲要拖住我<br />\n好好咁講分手唔得既<br />\n比左好多次機會，到我發現曬所有<br />\n我接受唔到話分手<br />\n你竟然可以一句道歉都冇<br />\n仲鬧返我<br />\n當我是甚麼"},{"pid":"18096992e3454c92432d9e96780b7bcf0c2bf780","tid":1084501,"uid":39885,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:50:02.000Z","msg":"廢話"},{"pid":"bf4a823792a3b01a7829e383c5555d19d15ed492","tid":1084501,"uid":189818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n拍拖兩年 <br />\n分咗手先比fd話我知 佢帽咗我年半<br />\n拍拖一直都對我唔好<br />\n分咗手我而家仲開心<br />\n多謝佢放過我"},{"pid":"69cbe84caba635ab233506536189cf2491dd16c7","tid":1084501,"uid":167465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:55:23.000Z","msg":"試過 我明白你感受 愛過痛苦 <br />\n人會好快成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119ef57563c584326b37e530e59cfec1a9d1c938","tid":1084501,"uid":155628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:12:40.000Z","msg":"恭喜你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成長咗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n識玩啦以後"},{"pid":"851ce1a66254794c861de84f3d17ce0d48e3ea4a","tid":1084501,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:13:20.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caceaf46a66f1e23089e667b301cb597f1a67c36","tid":1084501,"uid":230285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf4a823792a3b01a7829e383c5555d19d15ed492